== Adding a YouTube URL to the "Loading Cubes" loading screen. ==

A little while ago, a friend of mine was talking about the "[[Loading Screens#Cosmetics|Loading Cubes]]" loading screen and wanted to see it, however, it didn't seem like it was uploaded anywhere, especially after it was removed in-game.

I had a video on hand when I wanted to share the loading screen to a small group, so I have since uploaded the video to YouTube and it could be used to get an idea what this loading screen looked like and the music accompanying it.

